00:37:10,962 --> 00:37:13,965
I'm going to wash the camera footage around here. I'm requesting your support.

602
00:37:13,965 --> 00:37:17,969
(Ebihara) One of the remaining members of the Yui Yagami kidnapping group ➡

603
00:37:17,969 --> 00:37:21,973
There have been reports that Kenji Yamaguchi has once again kidnapped and confined people.

