00:37:21,973 --> 00:37:25,977
Daisuke Hayashida, who has been wanted for some time, has not yet been secured.

605
00:37:25,977 --> 00:37:28,479
Secure two people as soon as possible.

606
00:37:28,479 --> 00:37:30,982
Let's finish it! (All) Yes!

607
00:37:30,982 --> 00:37:33,484
Here it is.

608
00:37:33,484 --> 00:37:34,984
yes.

